3 Model fit

fit.gprior = bas.lm(V1 ~ .,
                     data = DF,
                     method = "MCMC", # better than default "BAS"
                                      # for large p
                     prior = "ZS-null", # default
                                        # "JZS" also can use
                     modelprior = uniform(),
                     include.always = ~1,
                     MCMC.iterations = 10000)
plot(fit.gprior, ask = F)
